column5: Hi Y'all Jest thought I'd show y'all some pictures of my kitty, Kiki Kat. I think he's real special.   Surveyin' his Kingdom..   After some Menu Foods Catnip (Jes kiddin' fellers!)   That's all fer now Y'all. I gotta go wrestle Jethro.
She'd make great bait!... Hmmmm.... for some reason her brows look somewhat like Lews...? Coincidence? I think not!! Bucktails!!!!  Gerritt.
Crazy Top-Water Feline Action!  Sorry Clampet, it's the alcohol talking.  :-)
Y'know, Jed...I always cringe when you misspell your own daughter's name. It's 'ELLY MAY'!
I know, Elly. And please tell him to  spell his last name properly. There are TWO 'T's in the Clampett name. Clampett is a nice name. 'Clampet' on the other hand, sounds like a plumbing device.
Paul  Crappie fishing very soon,  r u interested in going in the near future  Dave
If you don't mind me saying so, I think it might be time to give your Pussy a little trim Elly May ... startin to look just a little too much like BAIT !
